{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/issues/globally-quoted-identifiers-option-error","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"4f884ad0-b5a9-5789-a53a-d8783ad0efbb","html":"<p>아래와 같이 <code class=\"language-text\">application</code>이라는 엔티티와 테이블을 만들었습니다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"sql\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-light\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">CREATE TABLE application ();</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"kotlin\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-light\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">@Entity\n@Table(\n    name = &quot;application&quot;,\n    uniqueConstraints = [UniqueConstraint(columnNames = [&quot;key&quot;])],\n)\nclass ApplicationJpaEntity()</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>어플리케이션 구동시 ddl-auto는 validate로 설정해두었습니다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"yaml\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-light\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">spring:\n  jpa:\n    hibernate:\n      ddl-auto: validate</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>위와 같이 설정하고, 테이블을 미리 생성해 테이블이 있는것을 Sequel Pro로 확인했음에도 불구하고\n아래와 같은 에러가 지속적으로 발생했습니다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"bash\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-light\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">Schema-validation: missing table [application]</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h2 id=\"해결-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"해결 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결 방법</h2>\n<p>명확한 원인을 직접 코드 레벨로 파악한 것은 아니지만\n이름이 예약어와 겹치면서 문제가 발생하는 것 같았습니다.\n아래 옵션을 추가해 문제를 해결했습니다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code language=\"yaml\" terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-light\"  >\n          <code slot=\"code\">hibernate:\n  globally_quoted_identifiers: true\n  globally_quoted_identifiers_skip_column_definitions: true</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">globally_quoted_identifiers</code>옵션을 true로 지정하면 컬럼이나 테이블의 이름이 예약어와 충돌하는 것을 방지할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>해당 옵션을 추가하면 컬럼, 테이블 이름을 Back Quote(`)로 감싸주게 됩니다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>충돌 방지를 위해 globally<em>quoted</em>identifiers 옵션을 추가했는데 이후 아래와 같은 예외가 발생하는 경우가 있습니다.</p>\n<deckgo-highlight-code  terminal=\"carbon\" theme=\"one-light\"  highlight-lines=\"undefined\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">Caused by: org.hibernate.tool.schema.spi.SchemaManagementException: Schema-validation: wrong column type encountered in column</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n</blockquote>\n<p>이는 <code class=\"language-text\">globally_quoted_identifiers</code> 옵션 사용 시 columnDefinition에 있는 단어들도 함께 escape 되면서 발생하는 에러입니다.</p>\n<p>위와 같은 에러를 방지하기 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">globally_quoted_identifiers_skip_column_definitions</code> 옵션을 추가로 설정해주는 것이 좋습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://kwonnam.pe.kr/wiki/java/hibernate/configuration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://kwonnam.pe.kr/wiki/java/hibernate/configuration</a></p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/issues/globally-quoted-identifiers-option-error/#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">해결 방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/posts/issues/globally-quoted-identifiers-option-error/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/issues/globally-quoted-identifiers-option-error","tagSlugs":["/tag/jpa/","/tag/spring/","/tag/schema-validation/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","description":"globally_quoted_identifiers 옵션 적용 후 SchemaManagementException가 발생하는 경우","tags":["JPA","Spring","Schema-validation"],"title":"테이블이 존재하는데도 Schema-validation missing table 예외가 발생하는 경우","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/3fb2d4de4502fbae8b21ee45fe945cf4/kyucumber.jpg"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/issues/globally-quoted-identifiers-option-error"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2067870509","251939775","401334301"]}